reviewText:
The HS Boys are at it again in this epic film.

I've been a cutter, never so much of a strutter, but I do take pride in knowing the HS  Boys are at the top of their game and this film proves it.

Finally...the answer to the question we've all asked again and again..."How can I be a better cutter to take down a strutter?"

We all knew that 11 Cuttin' and Struttin' Videos could never satisfy our desires...but thanks to the HS Family...we now have 'Cuttin' & Struttin' XII!
